    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically robust example of the high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L straight-six features a 12.5:1 compression ratio and individual throttle bodies, delivering linear power to its 8,000 RPM redline. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including the VANOS solenoid refresh and professional subframe reinforcement. The chassis remains composed with upgraded Bilstein dampers and poly-bushings, ensuring the factory M-Variable limited-slip differential provides maximum corner-exit traction. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain is synchronized perfectly with a short-throw 6-speed manual, offering a pure tactile experience for the serious driver.",
