    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-maintained, reliable driver. The exterior paint retains a beautiful luster, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch, consistent with light, everyday use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in; the leather seats have been regularly conditioned to prevent cracking, and the carpets are free of stains. All power features, including the sunroof, heated seats, and the infotainment system, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in great shape. It has a documented service history, including a recent oil change and a cooling system flush. The transmission shifts smoothly, and the suspension remains tight and responsive. With tires at roughly 70% tread and brake pads recently replaced, this car is ready for the road with no immediate maintenance required.",
