    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it's totally ready for all your upcoming adventures! Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a weekend road trip, this beauty handles the road like a charm. I've taken great care of it, and I'm sure you're going to love it just as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions!",
